nodes.text: Unidentified Mon Calamari member of Grey Squadron

A Mon Calamari individual was a member of Grey Squadron, a New Republic military unit led by the Force-sensitive clone X2. At some point between the years 4 ABY and 19 ABY, the Mon Calamari accompanied X2 and the rest of Grey Squadron on a mission to the planet Dathomir. There, the Mon Calamari assisted X2 in clearing out the base that had once belonged to X2's brother, X1.
